lead_paragraph: Long-hitting American Gary Woodland, benefiting from a timely tune-up with his swing coach in Las Vegas last week, charged into a one-shot lead after the second round of the OHL Classic at Mayakoba in Mexico on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Woodland Takes Over at the Top in Mexico
headline.main: Woodland Takes Over at the Top in Mexico
